---
const target = "/admin/";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Write</title>
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content={`0;url=${target}`} />
    <link rel="canonical" href={`https://pangil5634.github.io${target}`} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>문서 작성 화면으로 이동 중입니다. <a href={target}>바로가기</a></p>
    <script>
      window.location.replace("/admin/");
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
